song_name: Rumors Of My Demise Have Been Greatly Exaggerated

version_description: All chords variations are marked as they appear in the original song.
This version is different to the original because it's lvie and it is also harder to play. In my opinion it sounds much better so I want to let you know how it gets played.
I beleive this is the correct way to play this with open chords in the first position if you do not want to play the original power chord version.
For easier version, put capo on the first fret and transpose -1. You can replace all the chords with corresponding power chords.
This is an acoustic version of the song, played in this video: Live Acoustic Version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7hmlSWzY4E.
